many.","year":33},{"id":"recqrovdvRBNSCMWs","ref":"Mark.13.7","text":"And when ye shall hear of wars and rumours of wars, be ye not troubled: for such things must needs be; but the end shall not be yet.","year":33},{"id":"recEyGi3CRHRBuVtE","ref":"Mark.13.8","text":"For nation shall rise against nation, and kingdom against kingdom: and there shall be earthquakes in divers places, and there shall be famines and troubles: these are the beginnings of sorrows.","year":33}]}
